AFRICAN NEWS AGENCY (ANA) ILINGANISELWA ku-R49 billion imali yombuso eyasetshenziswa ngokungafanele ngokulawulwa koMbuso yidlanzana, ngokusho komqondisi we-Shadow World, uMnuz Paul Edward Holden,  ngokophenyo olwenziwe. Lo mqondisi ukusho lokhu kwikhomishini eholwa nguJaji Raymond Zondo izolo. Ngokwakhe, bathola ukuthi imali engu-R49 157 323 233.68 yayilokhu ifakwa emabhange ahlukene. U-Holden ukusho lokhu efakaza ngemali eyayifakwa iphinde ikhishwe emabhange ahlukene. Ohola ubufakazi, u-Advocate Matthew Chaskalson, uyena obephonsa imibuzo uHolden. U-Holden utshele ikhomishini ukuthi ubufakazi bakhe bugxile emibikweni nangendlela imali ebikhokhwa ngayo emabhizinisini akwaGupta. Uveze ukuthi abakwaGupta bashushumbisa u-R287 million, abawuthola kwi-Estina Dairy Farm Project. Uhlelo kwakungelokuthuthukisa abalimi baseFree State. U-Holden uthe abakwaGupta baqala ukushushumbisa imali kusasele unyaka ukuba uhlelo lwase-Estina luqale. Uhulumeni waseFree State waqala ukukhokhela uhlelo lwase-Estina ngoJuni 2011 kodwa abakwaGupta baqala ukushushumbisa imali abathi bayithola kulolu hlelo ngoMeyi 2011. “Basebenzisa uhlelo lwase-Estina ukucasha beshushumbisa imali, ngaphambi kokuba lolu hlelo luqale,” kusho uHolden. Ngokobufakazi, kuvele ukuthi uhulumeni wakhokha u-R287 million kulo mndeni wakwaGupta, imali yabe isifakwa kuma-account ahlukene enkampani ukuze kubukeke sengathi wenza inzuzo ka-R880million phakathi kuka-2012 kuya ku-2016. Ikhomishini iyaqhubeka. 